OL,6,FThey're bad, we're good. That, in a
OL,7,Fnutshell, is the simplicity of
OL,8,Felection tactics from political
OL,9,Fparties.
OL,11,FBrand your opponents as the ones who
OL,12,Fwill plunge the country into darkness
OL,13,Fand despair, and present your party as
OL,14,Fthe saviours, leading the nation to
OL,15,Fthe sunlit uplands.
