OL,3,CSunak makes attack the best form of
OL,4,Cdefence
OL,6,FAttack, attack, attack. It may be
OL,7,Fcrude, but it has been proven to work
OL,8,Fin election after election. Present
OL,9,Fyour positive vision, yes, but then
OL,10,F'go negative' as political operatives
OL,11,Fsay.
OL,13,FWhich is pretty much what we heard
OL,14,Ffrom the Prime Minister today at the
OL,15,FScottish Tory conference in Aberdeen.
