OL,3,CSunak makes attack the best form of
OL,4,Cdefence
OL,6,FHere's a flavour of that from Rishi
OL,7,FSunak's speech today: "It is the
OL,8,FScottish Conservatives who are
OL,9,Fopposing the SNP making Scotland the
OL,10,Fmost taxed part of the United Kingdom.
OL,11,FWhile the Conservative government is
OL,12,Fcutting tax for every worker in
OL,13,FBritain, the Nationalists are raising
OL,14,Ftax on everyone who earns more than
OL,15,F#28,000 a year."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
