OL,3,CSunak makes attack the best form of
OL,4,Cdefence
OL,6,FHe added: "And it is only the Scottish
OL,7,FConservatives who are defending our
OL,8,Fenergy security, and the thousands of
OL,9,Fjobs here in the North East that
OL,10,Fdepend on the oil and gas sector. A
OL,11,Fvote for anyone else is a vote to shut
OL,12,Fdown this industry."
OL,14,FNow the SNP would argue that they have
OL,15,Fput up income tax in Scotland for the
OL,16,Fbetter off to pay for better public
OL,17,Fservices.And they would say they are
OL,18,Fthe true champions of the oil and gas
OL,19,Findustry with their plans for what
OL,20,Fthey call a 'just transition' - away
OL,21,Ffrom hydrocarbons to green energy.
