OL,3,CSunak makes attack the best form of
OL,4,Cdefence
OL,6,FWe've already heard attacks - that
OL,7,Fword again - on the Tories from Humza
OL,8,FYousaf and his colleagues, and we can
OL,9,Fexpect more to come.
OL,11,FLikewise Labour will attack (yes, you
OL,12,Fget the idea) the Conservatives at
OL,13,FWestminster and the SNP in Holyrood,
OL,14,Fclaiming Scotland has been let down by
OL,15,Fher two governments.
OL,17,FThe Prime Minister's aim today was to
OL,18,Fattack and to open up differences
OL,19,Fbetween his party and Labour and the
OL,20,FSNP.
