OL,6,FSo on tax, he claimed the Tories cut
OL,7,Ftaxes. They have recently, but as Paul
OL,8,FJohnson of the Institute for Fiscal
OL,9,FStudies has shown taxation is at an
OL,10,Fall-time high
OL,12,FAnd it is true that the SNP has put up
OL,13,Fincome taxes for higher earners,
OL,14,Fbeyond the levels south of the Border,
OL,15,Fcreating a differential across the
OL,16,FScotland-England border in the heart
OL,17,Fof our region.
