OL,4,Cdefence
OL,6,FThat does create a substantial
OL,7,Fdifference between the SNP and the
OL,8,FConservatives, which might be widened
OL,9,Fafter the UK budget on Tuesday.
OL,11,FToday there was a clear hint from the
OL,12,FPrime Minister - and from Scottish
OL,13,FSecretary and Dumfries and Galloway MP
OL,14,FAlister Jack - that if there are tax
OL,15,Fcuts it will be through National
OL,16,FInsurance, not income tax.
OL,18,FBecause National Insurance cuts apply
OL,19,Fnorth and south of the Border.
