OL,3,CSunak makes attack the best form of
OL,4,Cdefence
OL,6,FRishi Sunak even called the cuts that
OL,7,Fcame in in the new year "a Union tax
OL,8,Fcut" to emphasise the point.
OL,10,FDuring a question and answer session
OL,11,Fwith journalists the PM also said that
OL,12,FMr Jack had been a strong advocate of
OL,13,Fthis in the cabinet.
OL,15,FMr Jack added he had "made that point
OL,16,Fto the Chancellor". And I understand
OL,17,Fthat Mr Jack has also urged Jeremy
OL,18,FHunt to do the same next Tuesday.
