OL,6,FSo if there are to be tax cuts - and
OL,7,Fthere is a pre-election political
OL,8,Fimperative for the Tories to do that
OL,9,Feven if it puts pressure on public
OL,10,Ffinances and will be paid for by cuts
OL,11,Felsewhere - they will be in National
OL,12,FInsurance.
OL,14,FIt will be presented not only as a
OL,15,F'Union tax cut' but a cut in what the
OL,16,FPrime Minister described National
OL,17,FInsurance as - a tax on jobs.
