OL,6,FA by-product, which the Tories rather
OL,7,Fenjoy as it increased pressure on the
OL,8,FSNP, is that an NI cut results in no
OL,9,Fextra money for the Scottish
OL,10,Fgovernment, whereas an income tax cut
OL,11,Fwould mean extra cash, under the
OL,12,Fcomplicated funding system for
OL,13,Fdevolution.So far, so much the SNP v
OL,14,FLabour fight.
OL,16,FWhat of Labour?
