OL,6,FLabour in Scotland is now against any
OL,7,Fincome tax rises. And in the UK it
OL,8,Fhas, generally, accepted what the Tory
OL,9,Fgovernment has done -fearing that the
OL,10,FTories would attack (yes) Keir Starmer
OL,11,Fas a tax-raising Prime Minister in
OL,12,Fwaiting.
OL,14,FWe'll have to wait to see what Labour
OL,15,Fsays on budget day, though there will
OL,16,Fwithout a doubt be fierce criticism
OL,17,F(let's use a different word) of the
OL,18,FTories.
